('Friendship Peak Expedition', 'Technical climbing expedition to 5,289m peak in Pir Panjal range.', '/placeholder.svg?height=300&width=400', '12 Days', 'Very Difficult', 28000.00, 'Mountaineering expedition combining trekking and technical climbing skills to reach Friendship Peak summit.', ARRAY['Technical mountaineering', 'Rope and ice climbing', 'High-altitude camping', 'Mountaineering certification'], 'Only for experienced climbers with previous mountaineering experience and technical skills.', '{"day1": "Manali to Solang", "day2": "Solang to Dhundi", "day3": "Dhundi to Beas Kund", "day4": "Establish higher camps"}'::jsonb, 'Drive from Delhi to Manali. Technical briefing and equipment check mandatory.', 'Mountaineering course certificate required. Equipment rental available. Weather dependent.', ARRAY['Mountaineering equipment', 'Technical climbing gear', 'High-altitude clothing', 'Safety equipment', 'Personal climbing gear']),

