('Yoga & Meditation Retreat In The Himalayas', 'Combine trekking with yoga and meditation in serene Himalayan settings.', '/placeholder.svg?height=300&width=400', '7 Days', 'Easy', 15000.00, 'Rejuvenating experience combining gentle trekking with daily yoga sessions and meditation in pristine mountain environment.', ARRAY['Daily yoga sessions', 'Meditation practices', 'Himalayan serenity', 'Wellness focus'], 'Suitable for all levels. Focus on wellness and spiritual growth rather than physical challenge.', '{"day1": "Arrival and orientation", "day2": "Gentle trek with yoga", "day3": "Meditation and nature walks", "day4": "Advanced practices"}'::jsonb, 'Peaceful location accessible by road. Detailed location provided upon booking.', 'All-inclusive retreat. Vegetarian meals provided. Suitable for beginners.', ARRAY['Comfortable clothes', 'Yoga mat', 'Meditation cushion', 'Light trekking shoes', 'Personal items']),

('Leh Ladakh Multi-Sports Trip', 'Adventure sports combination including trekking, cycling, and river rafting in Ladakh.', '/placeholder.svg?height=300&width=400', '10 Days', 'Moderate to Difficult', 32000.00, 'Multi-activity adventure including trekking, mountain biking, river rafting, and cultural exploration in Ladakh.', ARRAY['Multiple adventure sports', 'Cultural immersion', 'Diverse landscapes', 'Comprehensive experience'], 'For adventure enthusiasts with good fitness levels and sporting experience.', '{"day1": "Leh arrival and acclimatization", "day2": "Local sightseeing and cycling", "day3": "River rafting on Indus", "day4": "Multi-day trek begins"}'::jsonb, 'Fly to Leh. Mandatory acclimatization period included in itinerary.', 'Multi-activity package. Equipment provided. Weather and water level dependent.', ARRAY['Sports clothing', 'Trekking boots', 'Sun protection', 'Personal gear', 'Adventure equipment provided']);

